{"tid":2082790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【傳承的愛】一週年追悼會：為了悼念因抗爭而離去的手足","createTime":"2020-06-28T10:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T16:58:22.000Z","uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"97b3feb3a679615a498279142b00dfe3efeebc97","tid":2082790,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T10:09:13.000Z","msg":"【傳承的愛】一週年追悼會<br />\n<br />\n目的：為了悼念因抗爭而離去的手足<br />\n日期：6月28號（星期日）<br />\n時間：晚上6點-9點<br />\n地點：九龍佑寧堂(油麻地佐敦道4號)<br />\n內容：嘉賓分享（阮民安等)，台灣手足分享，詩歌，祈禱<br />\n（設有獻花位置，由於室內位置不足，市民當天可以流水式獻花）<br />\n（好鄰舍北區教會facebook專頁會同時進行網上直播）<br />\n<br />\n合辦：<br />\n好鄰舍北區教會<br />\n傳承的愛籌委會<br />\n______________________________________<br />\n<br />\n【一週年追悼會 悼念信投稿】 <br />\n【傳承的愛一週年追悼會】<br />\n誠邀網民投稿 ，寫下一封悼念信。無論是想為手足打氣，還是祝願逝去者安息，我們都希望你能留下字句，你的心聲將有機會在追悼會當日被讀出。不要吝嗇你的一字一句，一同為手足打氣，也同時願逝去者安息。「你未走完的路，讓我代你走下去」。 <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/17oxT3yQJND3gVMoA3RauMcAm87Bt1dG1NMho2ctauLA/viewform?edit_requested=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F17oxT3yQJND3gVMoA3RauMcAm87Bt1dG1NMho2ctauLA%2Fviewform%3Fedit_requested%3Dtrue&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=605d403f\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/17oxT3yQJND3gVMoA3RauMcAm87Bt1dG1NMho2ctauLA/viewform?edit_requested=true</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nxhtTcE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnxhtTcE.jpg&h=26c6adc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f325886152cb68ce9ed2059ba0e5be66579c0923","tid":2082790,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T10:09:30.000Z","msg":"Live by White Night<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKWhiteNight/videos/1115022202199434/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKWhiteNight%2Fvideos%2F1115022202199434%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=3d628907\" target=\"